snippet.textDisplay: This is so amazing!! Transforming a hip-hop song into epic metal is such a hard task. I already commented on your Lightbringer and Mortal Reminder covers, and I have to say this is up there with those covers! I saw the cover of GODS by NewJeans with "more electric guitars" and it sounded really cool!  I really would be grateful if you did a rock/metal cover of that song, it'd be pretty cool too to see you guys in LoL cosplay. Anyways, love the cover as usual!
